eir hot takes on Apple&#8217;s &#8220;Scary Fast&#8221; event. They dissect the unveiling of the new iMacs, the remarkable M3 MacBook Pros, and mull over the conspicuous absence of a Mac mini announcement. As they deep dive into the Mac&#8217;s gaming potential, highlighting titles like Minecraft, Hearthstone, and Kerbal Space Program, the trio speculates about a novel gaming platform on the horizon. And while they&#8217;re at it, there&#8217;s a candid conversation on Intel&#8217;s latest moves and its potential trajectory. Remember, in the ever-evolving tech landscape, &#8220;Don&#8217;t Get Caught&#8221; out of the loop. Tune in and stay informed!</p>
